{"tid":2515994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海外IP未能登入港台網站 港台稱伺服器故障","createTime":"2021-05-04T10:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T10:50:04.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"80f40633af37d1d9c1b246646079635bbfc399cc","tid":2515994,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:50:04.000Z","msg":"有海外人士稱未能登入網站 港台：伺服器一度短暫故障<br />\n<br />\n有身處海外的人士反映，今日一度未能登入港台網站，只顯示白色畫面。<br />\n<br />\n港台發言人表示，中午後港台其中一組伺服器出現短暫及局部故障，因此曾影響一些用戶進入港台網站，經搶修後服務已回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589185-20210504.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589185-20210504.htm&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=c872085d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589185-20210504.htm&h=0c58093a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589185-20210504.htm</a>"}]}